cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with the problem of detecting fake images generated by CNN-based models. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper involves machine learning techniques and models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the limitations of CNN-generated images, which could make it relevant to cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
